</td>
<td valign="top" width="360">
<p class="normal">data protection, ethics, privacy</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" valign="top" width="442">
<p class="normal"><strong>Policy Context</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
