<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Slade, Sharon and Prinsloo, Paul (2014). Student perspectives on the use of their data: between intrusion, surveillance and care. In: <em>Challenges for Research into Open &amp; Distance Learning: Doing Things Better &ndash; Doing Better Things</em>, pp. 291&ndash;300.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
