              <title>LAEP Inventory: Policies</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9630</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/9630</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<div class="user-entry">
<div class="user-entry">
<div class="user-entry">
<p>This section of the LAEP Inventory brings together learning analytics policies.</p>
<p>The LAEP Inventory is used to collect evidence of practical implementations of learning analytics in the context of education, and to document the state of the art. The Inventory is split into three sections, and each of these has its own cloud and cloudscape.</p>
<ul>
<li>Tools</li>
<li>Practices</li>
<li>Policy documents</li>
</ul>
<p>The Inventory has been developed using existing academic literature, policy documents, practitioner-generated reports (grey literature) and contributions from the learning analytics community.</p>
