<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; change, politics &amp; education<br /> <a href="http://www.hihohiho.com/newthinking/edctnmngrph34.pdf">www.hihohiho.com/new thinking/edctnmngrph34.pdf</a></p>
